    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 25 \u2014 SLA Breach Monitor & Escalation\n\n**Env variables needed:**\n- ZENDESK_EMAIL: your Zendesk admin email\n- ZENDESK_API_TOKEN: from Zendesk Admin > API\n- PAGERDUTY_ROUTING_KEY: from PagerDuty service integration\n\n**Update:** Replace YOUR_SUBDOMAIN in both HTTP nodes with your Zendesk subdomain.\n\n**SLA targets:** Edit the SLA_TARGETS object in the Code node to match your actual SLA commitments.\n\n**Deduplication:** Add a HubSpot or Redis check before the Slack nodes to prevent re-alerting on the same ticket every 15 minutes.",
        "height": 240,
        "width": 420
      },
